This code should be considered very much as work-in-progress.
Any part of this release could be subject to change.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

  openssl
  
  (download from www.openssl.org)


* For any question try to write to the author: fanton@exentrica.it
